The app we are going to make is an SMS text blaster.

The core features must include:
Integration with SMS gateway API
Contact list management
Message scheduling and queuing
Delivery status tracking
Templates for frequently sent messages

We need to:
Use third-party services to send an dreceive SMS messages/
Organize recipients intro groups and tags for trargeted messaging.
Allow messages to be sent at a later time or in batches.
Confirm which messages were sent, devliered, or failed.
Save and reuse standard message formats



The stack we are using is:
Express  
Sveltekit (Strictly use Typescript)
Mysql
Vonage for sms